 "textcontent_l43gjokd7a_html": "Shipping",
 "textcontent_fbxcsdr13ui_html": "AnimalPride.com offers FREE shipping on all orders over $35! We ship all orders within 1 business day, and we use priority shipping with USPS or UPS to ensure you have tracking on your order.<div><br><\/div><div>Our dedicated staff located in Jacksonville, FL takes pride in getting your order shipped to you as fast as possible with the utmost care. Our business days are Monday-Friday, excluding holidays.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We also offer expedited shipping options (2nd Day Air, Next Day Air) through UPS, which is available for purchase during checkout.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>We currently ship only within the United States. We do not ship internationally at this time.<div><div><\/div><\/div><\/div>",
