 "textcontent_ekdc5shtk4t_html": "We want you to love your purchase! Animal Pride\u2122 is 100% committed to your satisfaction and is happy to offer a hassle-free return process.<div><br><\/div><div>If you are not completely satisfied, please let us know and we'll work with you to make it right.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>To initiate a return, exchange, or cancellation, please email <a href=\"mailto:support@animalpride.com\">support@animalpride.com<\/a> and write your order number in the subject line (for example please write: \"Return Request for 2102-AP\"). You will receive further instructions within one business day. Our business days are Monday-Friday, excluding holidays.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>&nbsp;Please keep in mind, returned items should be unused and in the same condition that you received them. We do offer refunds.<div><div><\/div><\/div><\/div>",
